 are and should<br />\n  continue after June 30, 1997, to be the policy of the United States with<br />\n  respect to commerce between the United States and Hong Kong:<br />\n<br />\n (8) The United States should continue to support access by Hong Kong to<br />\n  sensitive technologies controlled under the agreement of the Coordinating<br />\n  Committee for Multilateral Export Controls (commonly referred to as `COCOM')<br />\n  <span style=\"color: red;\">for so long as the United States is satisfied that such technologies are<br />\n  protected from improper use or export</span>."},{"pid":"630054c990e2873bee7af0b4243446b43b0d832f","tid":631882,"uid":158936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T10:14:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3ba5a078102adad0ac0837bda62efafc8d74642c","tid":631882,"uid":105445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"317fe94dc7694555744d6a75e0dfe7268f264e41","tid":631882,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"31d9f9014ecd85e2bc2893f92f538c20eeb56497","tid":631882,"uid":105445,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"da9d3025710d22f85759606ab600b3acfd912544","tid":631882,"uid":5490,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T07:57:20.000Z","msg":"無錢出糧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T07:59:55.000Z","msg":"仲有5g都玩撚完了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T09:33:25.000Z","msg":"姐係香港都冇5g ?"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T10:16:43.000Z","msg":"係 而家美國要打擊中國全部IT行業 5G應該會延遲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a44ea6e0989c2d73c3a3adc337ebece72131f9de","tid":631882,"uid":141151,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T10:17:08.000Z","msg":"SEC. 201. CONTINUED APPLICATION OF UNITED STATES LAW.<br />\n  (a) IN GENERAL- Notwithstanding any change in the exercise of sovereignty<br />\n  over Hong Kong, the laws of the United States shall continue to apply with<br />\n  respect to Hong Kong, on and after July 1, 1997, in the same manner as the<br />\n  laws of the United States were applied with respect to Hong Kong before<br />\n  such date unless otherwise expressly provided by law or by Executive order<br />\n  under section 202.<br />\n<br />\nSEC. 202. PRESIDENTIAL ORDER.<br />\n  (a) PRESIDENTIAL DETERMINATION- On or after July 1, 1997, whenever the<br />\n  President determines that Hong Kong is not sufficiently autonomous to justify<br />\n  treatment under a particular law of the United States, or any provision<br />\n  thereof, different from that accorded the People's Republic of China,<br />\n  the President may issue an Executive order suspending the application of<br />\n  section 201(a) to such law or provision of law.<br />\n<br />\n確立香港如同97前地位，同埋總統出行政指令suspend香港97前地位，兩者都係香港關係法內容<br />\n中興唔好害死香港呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a55db7785a0cb2249f92d36e418acc2628a7bfc9","tid":631882,"uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"3ba5a078102adad0ac0837bda62efafc8d74642c","tid":631882,"uid":105445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"317fe94dc7694555744d6a75e0dfe7268f264e41","tid":631882,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"31d9f9014ecd85e2bc2893f92f538c20eeb56497","tid":631882,"uid":105445,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T07:59:55.000Z","msg":"仲有5g都玩撚完了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T09:33:25.000Z","msg":"姐係香港都冇5g ?"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T10:16:43.000Z","msg":"係 而家美國要打擊中國全部IT行業 5G應該會延遲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T10:18:21.000Z","msg":"支那+HK No IT"},{"pid":"c92035c4fad9d5c041d274fdd8ff69255170586d","tid":631882,"uid":141151,"like":1,"dislike":0,